<H3> <TI>   Franco Ordered To Rest Because of Flu Symptoms </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY0802131094 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network in 
Portuguese 0900 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0802131094 </F>
<F P=104>  Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] President Itamar Franco today will resume his normal 
activities at Planalto Palace. Yesterday afternoon the 
president felt slightly ill and he was urged to spend the rest 
of the afternoon resting at Alvorada Palace. The president has 
flu symptoms. 

</TEXT>

