<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The foreign ministers of the Mercosur [Common 
Market of the South] countries will meet in Buenos Aires on 9 
March. 
  Uruguayan Foreign Minister Sergio Abreu reported that the 
foreign ministers of the Mercosur countries will review a 
Brazilian proposal to form a regional free trade zone and 
establish a common external tariff. 
