  [Text] Jean Guzman of the Haitian Revolutionary Party [PRH] 
condemns the decision of the Committee of Actions for National 
Reconciliation [CARENA]. The resolution is illegal, says Mr. 
Guzman, who recognizes only the authority of the head of the 
executive for the convening of a national conference: 
  [Begin recording, in Creole] Only the executive power, 
