the resolutions they have adopted are null and void. That is why 
we in the PRH call for mobilization of the entire Haitian people 
of the nine geographic departments to denounce these people who 
know very well that they are only aggravating the situation. The 
essential solution to the crisis resides in the agreement signed 
on Governors Island between President Jean-Bertrand Aristide and 
General Raoul Cedras. [end recording] 

