<F P=102>  PA1102013794 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 0000 GMT 11 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1102013794 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Azuzena Lievano from the "24 Hours" newscast] </F>
  [Text] After a nine-hour session, the State Council issued 
a six-line communique this afternoon stating their decision not 
to comment on what they described as an affront by the 
president. They announced their intention to leave the 
investigation of the military troops in Juanchaco in the hands 
of the appropriate authorities and to let the public make up its 
own mind about the president's reaction to the Council's 
decision on the presence of foreign troops in Colombia. 

</TEXT>

