Omar Morales Ramirez; Lieutenant Juan Ramirez Flores; Captain 
Ricardo Falconi Alvarez; Captain Ignacio Trauco Rojas, reserve 
status; and Subofficer 1st Class Jorge Santiesteban Chicoma. 
  For Selling Quotas to Coca Growers: Subofficer 2d Class 
Efrain Cerna Alfaro, reserve status; Lieutenant Miguel Velezmoro 
